@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}
<h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

<p>
    The videogame catalog application is designed under a principle of total respect for privacy. For your peace of mind, the handling of information is detailed below:

    Data Collection: We do not collect sensitive personal information. The data stored is limited exclusively to catalog management, such as videogame titles, genres, platforms, and images.

    Purpose: This information is used solely for organizational and personalized consultation purposes within the application interface.

    Third Parties: Your data is not shared with external entities nor used for commercial or advertising purposes.

    User Control: You retain ownership and control over the information you enter at all times, with the freedom to modify or delete it whenever you wish.

    Limitation of Liability: By using this service, you accept the terms above. Likewise, the administration is exempt from any responsibility regarding the integrity of the data in the event of force majeure, such as an apocalypse or an imminent war against Soviet bears.
</p>
